title: Entrance Initial Description
story: friendly-zoo
description: ADR-196 Phase 4 — entrance shows its first-visit (initial) description once, then the standard description on a re-look.
---

# First look at the entrance shows the first-visit-only flavor.
> look
[OK: contains "Your family piles out of the car"]

# A second look at the same room shows the STANDARD description, not the initial one.
> look
[OK: contains "wrought-iron gates"]
[OK: not contains "Your family piles out of the car"]
